OL,6,FThe unit price of gas is increasing
OL,7,Ffrom 6.34p per kilowatt-hour (kWh) to
OL,8,F6.99p per kWh, and electricity is
OL,9,Fgoing up from 24.86p/kWh to 27.03p/kWh.
OL,11,FHouseholds are urged to send an
OL,12,Faccurate meter reading to ensure that
OL,13,Fall energy they use before the higher
OL,14,Fprices come into effect is billed at
OL,15,Fthe lower rate.
OL,17,FIt is also sensible to check if it
OL,18,Fwould be worth switching to a fixed
OL,19,Ftariff, which works by locking in a
OL,20,Fset rate for gas and electricity for a
OL,21,Fspecific period such as 12 months.
