OL,6,FHouseholds in England and Wales will
OL,7,Fsee their water bills increase by an
OL,8,F"extortionate" average of #86 over the
OL,9,Fnext year alone.
OL,11,FRegulator Ofwat has allowed companies
OL,12,Fto raise average bills by 36%, or #157
OL,13,Fin total, over the next five years, to
OL,14,F#597 by 2030, to help finance a #104
OL,15,Fbillion upgrade for the sector.
